dct_description_sm: Municipal boundaries are shown. Includes 57 page guide booklet titled: Liberec, průvodce městem; containing descriptions of the city and street index. Includes inset of Vnitřní Město (scale 1:10,000). Vytiskla Severografia. Krajske Nakladatelstvi Liberec.
